## Journey Analytics & Insights

### Performance Metrics
- **Completion Rates**: Journey step completion statistics
- **Time to Completion**: Average time to complete each journey
- **Drop-off Points**: Common abandonment points
- **Success Indicators**: Key performance indicators for each journey

### Optimization Opportunities
- **Bottleneck Identification**: Journey step optimization
- **User Feedback Integration**: Continuous improvement based on user input
- **A/B Testing**: Journey variant testing and optimization
- **Personalization**: Customized journey experiences

